  "title": "Human Resource Head | Public Health | Central-West",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a local leading player in healthcare industry. They are now recruiting a Head of HR to be part of their HR team to assist the next phase of their business. They are located in the Central-West - easily accessible.</strong></p><p>Roles and Responsibilities of Head of HR:</p><ul><li>Lead and execute HR strategies to build a motivated, high-performing workforce for a new team.</li><li>Drive the planning and implementation of workforce build-up and deployment during the pre-operational phase.</li><li>Collaborate closely with department heads, and various stakeholders to deliver integrated and quality HR support.</li><li>Oversee all HR functions including:</li></ul><ol><li>Manpower planning and resourcing</li><li>Talent acquisition and development</li><li>Employee and industrial relations</li><li>Performance and rewards management</li><li>Talent management and succession planning</li><li>Leadership development and organizational design</li><li>Change management and staff retention strategies</li></ol><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min Degree holder with postgraduate qualification in HR</li><li>Min 10 years of HR management experience</li><li>Experience in stakeholder management</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email Address: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
